2015-11-01  Francisco Javier Dorado <javier@tiflolinux.org>

        * src/dbr.in:
          src/dbr.py:

           Handle situations where dbr is installed in other prefix
           or PYTHONPATH. Sets dbr entry point for DBR not dbr.py.

        * src/vista.py:

           Mark some missing strings for translation. Added control + space 
           for play/pause functionality, and control + n control + shift n 
           for page down and page up respectively.

